            Description 1054 Miramonte #14

            Looking for a 1 bedroom condo with breathtaking city and mountain views? This 2nd-floor unit offers panoramic views that will take your breath away. Whether you're enjoying your morning coffee or winding down after a long day, you'll be able to take in the beauty of the Santa Barbara landscape from the comfort of your own home.The HOA provides access to a club house and two pools, perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing on a sunny day.Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Santa Barbara.
